text: A magnitude 6.6 or 6.8 earthquake hit Luding County in Sichuan province, China on 5 September 2022. The epicenter was located from Chengdu. A total of 46 people died, 50 were injured and 16 were missing. ==References== Category:September 2022 events Category:2022 disasters in Asia Category:2022 earthquakes Category:2022 in China
title: 2022 Luding earthquake
